OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunshine
OL,6,Fthrough the evening, with plenty of
OL,7,Fclear skies overnight. Perhaps a few
OL,8,Fmist and fog patches forming as winds
OL,9,Ffall light during the early hours. A
OL,10,Fcooler night than of late.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FPlenty of sunshine through the
OL,13,Fday, once any morning shallow mist or
OL,14,Ffog patches clear. Feeling warmer for
OL,15,Fmany as winds remain light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
