OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FGenerally a cloudier day on Saturday
OL,7,Fwith drizzle over the Moors. Variable
OL,8,Fcloud with sunshine at times for
OL,9,FSunday and Monday. Temperatures
OL,10,Fgenerally above average, so feeling
OL,11,Fwarm.
